'''Barbara Umuhoza''' ni Pasiteri mu  [[Rwanda]] , umuhuza wa magambo , akora muri domene  zitandukanye ari umusemuzi mu ndimi zitandukanye, Umunyamakuru kandi akaba umushyushyarugamba (MC). Ni nyiri Éclat Communications Ltd, isosiyete itanga serivisi mubusemuzi, gutunganya ibintu no gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga. <ref>https://trailblazersimpact.com/season-three-ptb/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
'''Umuhoza''' kandi ni umwe mu bashinze umuryango wa Lucia's Scashed Candles, isosiyete IKORA  buji ihumura ikorerwa mu [[Rwanda]] kandi ikwirakwizwa mu gihugu . <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/duo-choosing-local-candle-making-spice-living-spaces</ref> Umuhoza ni umunyamuryango wa [[Rwanda]] Leaders Fellowship yakira gahunda zo gutanga inama ku rubyiruko mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/207106</ref> <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/Jeannette-Kagame-arashishikariza-urubyiruko-rw-abayobozi-kwigira-ku</ref> <ref>https://rwandaises.com/2020/01/umubano-mwiza-wabashakanye-ntupfa-kubaho-gusa-uraharanirwa-madamu-jeannette-kagame/</ref> Yakiriye iserukiramuco rya sinema rya gikirisitu ryo mu [[Rwanda]] 2018 <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/84145/rwanda-christian-film-festival-84145.html</ref> , maze ayobora ubwo barangizaga icyiciro cya 2019 mu kigo gishinzwe guteza imbere ubukungu bw’umugore (IEEW). Yagizwe moderator muri Alliance for Financial inclusion's 2019 Global Policy Forum . <ref>https://ieew.org/2019/10/around-the-class-of-2019-barbara-umuhoza/</ref> Muri 2020, yitabiriye inama y’amahoro binyuze mu bucuruzi iyobowe n’ikigo gishinzwe guteza imbere ubukungu bw’umugore aho yagejeje ibitekerezo bye ku nshingano z’ubushumba n’uburyo byagize ingaruka ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 . <ref>https://trailblazersimpact.com/season-three-ptb/</ref> <ref>https://trailblazersimpact.com/season-three-ptb/#</ref> Umuhoza asangira ibitekerezo bye abinyujije kuri podcasts yakirwa kuri IHeartRadio . <ref>https://www.iheart.com/podcast/263-peace-through-business-56252519/episode/ep16-barbara-umuhoza-pastor-and-successful-communications-56261452/</ref> Umuhoza kandi yashinze Barbara Show kuri YouTube hamwe na videwo mu [[Ikinyarwanda|Kinyarwanda]] hamwe na rimwe na rimwe mu Cyongereza. <ref>https://teakisi.com/content-i-have-been-enjoying/</ref>

